      Ferran Ram<span class="text-[3.88rem] font-normal sm:text-[5.2rem]">í</span>rez
    </h1>
    <h2 class="mb-6 font-heming text-4xl font-medium leading-[1.15] sm:text-5xl">
      <span class="indigo-wavy !decoration-[3px] !underline-offset-[5px]"> full stack</span> developer
    </h2>
    <p>
      {
        lang == "es" ? (
          <>
